{
  "high_level_description": "A haunting abstract illustration of a mother and child separated by an unseen force, rendered in dusty rose and sepia with gold leaf accents, their reaching arms converging toward a glowing central void without touching.",
  "compositional_deconstruction": {
    "background": "Vertical full-bleed painterly ground in muted dusty rose (#C9A89E) and warm sepia (#B08968), with soft fog-like haze diffusing across the field. Loose gestural brushwork with visible drag marks and dry-brush texture throughout. The atmosphere dissolves edges into the muted background rather than terminating them cleanly, evoking contemporary figurative abstraction.",
    "elements": [
      {
        "type": "obj",
        "desc": "Mother's elongated sinewy arm arcing diagonally from the upper-left quadrant down toward the center-right, rendered in fluid liquid brushstrokes of dusty rose and sepia. Fraying edges dissolve into surrounding haze. Fingers splayed open, reaching rightward toward the child, fingertips nearly meeting the central void."
      },
      {
        "type": "obj",
        "desc": "Smudged silhouette of a small child figure anchored in the lower-right quadrant, only partially formed. Soft charcoal-and-sepia smudge suggesting head and torso, one outstretched arm reaching leftward and upward toward the mother. Edges feather into the muted background."
      },
      {
        "type": "obj",
        "desc": "Glowing ethereal void along the central vertical axis between the two figures. A luminous pale-cream fissure where their fingertips nearly meet but never touch, faint warm glow bleeding outward into the surrounding haze. The unresolved gap is the compositional focal point."
      },
